flowchart LR
    A[Focused work on Change A] --> I[Interruption or review wait]
    I --> B[Work on Change B]
    B --> C[Return trigger for Change A]
    C --> R[Reconstruct code, decisions, and local state]
    R --> A2[Resume productive work]

    I -. attention residue .-> B
    B -. intervening changes .-> R
    C -. AI summary or preserved context .-> R
